column5: Happy birthday, hope you're having a decent day despite everything
Im so proud of you, you pulled through so much pain and it was worth it!
Well done im proud as hell
Thats great, I know it's really hard but I believe in you

It's never too late, I also wasted so much of my life not going out because I was too afraid of what people would think. If you can push yourself to do it, then I would say it's never too late to get out there and make memories
Good luck! I promise no one cares about how you present half as much as you might think they do, you got this!
Yup I'm definitely finding it difficult, I hope you're at a place where you're finding it easy
Thanks I hope so, I'm trying to keep on opening up anyway.
Thank you, that helps a lot, I appreciate it
